The Ghost Gate stands open, hiding unknown opportunities. You need to obtain the Iron Spear, Mountain Armor, and Battle Helmet to conceal your living aura and blend in with the Spectral Soldiers. Search carefully for these items.

If you encounter Spectral Soldiers, avoid them;
If you spot a lantern, that marks a path to safety;
If you meet a masked lantern bearer, you may seek assistance from them.

#RSet the time to the You hour (5-7 pm) to return to market hours.#E

Snow-haired, three thousand feet;
Fireworks, ten thousand layers.
Warhorses cry in Shangdu;
Dragons leap o'er distant seas.

